{"type":null,"faqId":46126,"title":"如何使用华为耳机控制音乐播放？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>荣耀7i支持三建耳机和智能线控功能，提供了以下控制方式：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、短按耳机中间按钮，控制音乐播放器在播放/暂停模式之间切换。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、连按两次耳机中间按钮，切换到下一首歌曲。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、连按三次耳机中间按钮，切换到上一首歌曲。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4、短按音量+键，为提高媒体播放音量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5、双击音量+键，为将当前歌曲添加“我喜欢“或从”我喜欢“中移除。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>6、长按音量+键，为分享当前播放的音频文件。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>7、短按音量-键，为降低媒体播放音量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>8、双击音量-键，为切换音乐列表播放顺序。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>9、长按音量-键，为下载当前播放的在线音乐。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果不开启智能线控，只有上面的1、2、3、4、7生效。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170745\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>请尽量使用华为原厂耳机，其他品牌的耳机可能和华为手机不兼容导致无法控制音乐播放。非华为音乐播放器可能不支持耳机控制播放，具体请咨询相关应用开发商。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1906","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376110000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":39,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为,耳机,控制","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}